text: Wanda Marie Allan-Parsons is an archer from Canada. Allan competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics.Wanda ALLAN-SADEGUR She was born on 24 January 1955.Wanda Allan-Sadegur == References == Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian archers Category:Olympians for Canada
